    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve taken care of all the essentials, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
