    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the power band. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement to ensure structural and internal longevity. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a suspension geometry that preserves its legendary handling characteristics. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the drivetrain is robust, providing a visceral, high-RPM analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance history. No mechanical issues. Interior and exterior are well-kept.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical of careful use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned, showing only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s seat. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is sound, featuring a comprehensive service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. Most recently, the brake pads were replaced and the tires rotated, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride with a responsive transmission and no known mechanical issues. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking reliability and aesthetic appeal without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents an exceptional opportunity for the sophisticated driver. Presenting in commendable condition, the automobile features a refined interior and a robust mechanical profile that ensures a superior driving experience. Every aspect of this vehicle has been vetted to meet our dealership's exacting standards for performance and longevity. We invite you to secure this distinguished example of automotive excellence, which offers an ideal balance of prestige and proven reliability.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
