    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and is totally ready for a new home. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you can just hop in and go! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the high-revving power is delivered reliably to the rear wheels. The suspension remains tight with upgraded poly-bushings, providing exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. While showing some honest patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is robust, making it the perfect candidate for a weekend canyon carver or a dedicated enthusiast build.",
